## Quick Reference: Before → After

| Vanilla JS | HTMX/Alpine Replacement |
|-----------|------------------------|
| `fetch('/url', {method: 'POST', body: ...})` | `<form hx-post="/url">` |
| `document.getElementById('x').innerHTML = y` | `hx-target="#x" hx-swap="innerHTML"` |
| `el.style.display = 'block'/'none'` | `x-show="condition"` |
| `el.addEventListener('click', fn)` | `@click="fn"` or `hx-trigger="click"` |
| `el.classList.add/remove/toggle()` | `:class="{ 'active': condition }"` |
| `clearTimeout(t); t = setTimeout(fn, 300)` | `hx-trigger="input changed delay:300ms"` |
| `JSON.parse(response)` then DOM update | Return HTML fragment from Django view |
